tosdr.case: Users shall not interfere with another person's enjoyment of the service

title: Users shall not interfere with another person's enjoyment of the service
quoteText:
It is not permitted to use the software in a manner that causes hindrance or a nuisance for other users.
In addition, you must not use the software in any way that is unlawful, illegal or harmful or for any purpose or activity in connection thereto.
